data.description: Great 5-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home on an expansive 1 acre lot, boasting breathtaking views of a serene lake, river and majestic mountains. Gorgeous panoramic sunset views. This residence features a spacious interior, complemented by a large garage for convenience and storage, that has a new roof with a 10 year warranty. Property has enough space to build an  very large RV Garage and Casita. Embrace a perfect blend of space and nature in this picturesque setting. Horses are allowed!
